## 🎨 Design System

| Élément | Valeur |
|---|---|
| Couleur primaire | `#F72585` (rose) |
| Couleur secondaire | `#4361EE` (bleu) |
| Gradient | `linear-gradient(135deg, #F72585, #4361EE)` |
| Border radius cards | `16px–24px` |
| Box shadow | `0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)` |
| Font | Inter (Google Fonts, déjà configuré) |
| Responsive | Style inline (`style={{}}`) — pas de classes Tailwind responsive |

